#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:12
msgid ""
"受限玻尔兹曼机（Restricted Boltzmann Machine, RBM）是一种基于能量的概率图模型，由可见层（Visible "
"Layer）和隐层（Hidden Layer）组成，层内无连接，层间全连接。其核心是通过无监督学习学习数据的潜在特征分布。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:15
msgid "1. 模型结构"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:17
msgid "**可见层（``v``）**：输入数据的显式表示（如像素值）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:18
msgid "**隐层（``h``）**：提取的潜在特征。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:19
msgid "**权重矩阵（``W``）**：连接可见层与隐层的权重。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:20
msgid "**偏置**：可见层偏置（``b``）和隐层偏置（``c``）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:23
msgid "2. 能量函数与概率分布"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:25
msgid "RBM 的能量函数定义为："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:27
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"E(\\mathbf{v}, \\mathbf{h}) = -\\mathbf{v}^T W \\mathbf{h} - "
"\\mathbf{b}^T \\mathbf{v} - \\mathbf{c}^T \\mathbf{h}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:31
msgid "联合概率分布通过玻尔兹曼分布给出："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:33
msgid ""
"P(\\mathbf{v}, \\mathbf{h}) = \\frac{ e^{-E(\\mathbf{v}, \\mathbf{h})} "
"}{Z}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:37
msgid "其中 :math:`Z` 为配分函数（归一化因子）。可见层的边缘分布为："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:39
msgid "P(\\mathbf{v}) = \\sum_{\\mathbf{h}} P(\\mathbf{v}, \\mathbf{h})"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:44
msgid "3. 条件独立性"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:46
msgid "由于层内无连接，给定可见层时隐层条件独立，反之亦然："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:48
#, python-brace-format
msgid "P(h_j=1|\\mathbf{v}) = \\sigma\\left(\\sum_i W_{ij} v_i + c_j\\right)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:52
#, python-brace-format
msgid "P(v_i=1|\\mathbf{h}) = \\sigma\\left(\\sum_j W_{ij} h_j + b_i\\right)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:56
msgid "其中 :math:`\\sigma(x) = \\frac{1}{1+e^{-x}}` 为 Sigmoid 激活函数。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:59
msgid "4. 训练目标"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:61
msgid "通过最大化似然函数学习参数（``W``, ``b``, ``c``）。目标函数为负对数似然："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:63
msgid "\\mathcal{L} = -\\sum_{\\mathbf{v}} \\log P(\\mathbf{v})"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:67
msgid "采用对比散度（CD）算法近似梯度，更新规则为："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:69
msgid ""
"\\Delta W_{ij} = \\epsilon \\left(\\langle v_i h_j "
"\\rangle_{\\text{data}} - \\langle v_i h_j "
"\\rangle_{\\text{recon}}\\right)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.rst:73
msgid ""
"其中 :math:`\\epsilon` 为学习率，:math:`\\langle \\cdot \\rangle_{\\text{data}}`"
" 和 :math:`\\langle \\cdot \\rangle_{\\text{recon}}` 分别为数据分布和重构分布的期望。"
msgstr ""

